---
title: Tuscan Meatloaf with Roasted Green Beans and Rosemary Mashed Potatoes
description: We’re not sure what we like best about this recipe: the flavorful herbs and spices in the ground meat, the fact that individual patties don’t take nearly as long as traditional meatloaf to cook, or the silky, melt-in-your-mouth mashed potatoes. We’ll let you (or your kids!) make the call.
